      "id": "PopularPost185327",
      "post_content": "@schoolmonkey: No, Pauper is correct. X is only \"set in stone\" on the stack if it's an X that you pay as a cost, like \"pay X mana\" or \"discard X cards\". If it's just \"Do X things, where X is some number\", then that's counted on resolution.  \n  \nFor example, an [Auriok Bladewarden](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Auriok Bladewarden) activation can be hosed by [Diminish](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Diminish) in response. People can up or down the amount that [Batttlefield Medic](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Batttlefield Medic) will prevent by killing or making Clerics at instant speed. And so on.  \n  \nI'm glad it does work that way, because [Zedruu the Greathearted](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Zedruu the Greathearted) is an awesome card :D",
      "posted_by": "alextfish",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost185327\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">@schoolmonkey: No, Pauper is correct. X is only \"set in stone\" on the stack if it's an X that you pay as a cost, like \"pay X mana\" or \"discard X cards\". If it's just \"Do X things, where X is some number\", then that's counted on resolution.<br/><br/>For example, an <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Auriok Bladewarden\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Auriok Bladewarden\">Auriok Bladewarden</a> activation can be hosed by <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Diminish\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Diminish\">Diminish</a> in response. People can up or down the amount that <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Batttlefield Medic\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Batttlefield Medic\">Batttlefield Medic</a> will prevent by killing or making Clerics at instant speed. And so on.<br/><br/>I'm glad it does work that way, because <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Zedruu the Greathearted\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Zedruu the Greathearted\">Zedruu the Greathearted</a> is an awesome card :D</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '185327'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy353\">alextfish</span>\r\n           